@instagibbs thanks for the review.

I updated the PR description to remove the follow-up ideas. Those don't belong in the PR description and are better suited to discussion in issues.

re: a limit to the number of transactions in the queue - I agree with @vasild and don't think it's a blocker for this change. But, if you insist I can add a commit to limit to 1000 transactions.

